IAB / Atmos Analysis Pipeline (current state)
--------------------------------------------
- Detect: is_atmos_file → flags ADM / IAB / MXF / EC3 / EAC3; IAB check includes .iab/.atmos names.
- IAB path:
  - Dolby Atmos Conversion Tool → ADM WAV (optional head trim via IAB_HEAD_DURATION_SECONDS)
  - soundfile downmix of ADM WAV to analysis WAV (fallback: continue to standard pipeline)
- Audio-only MXF:
  - ffmpeg extract → 48k stereo PCM WAV → analyze
- Other Atmos (MXF with video, EC3/EAC3/ADM):
  - convert_atmos_to_mp4 (copy/AAC; fallback WAV if needed) → ffmpeg extract stereo/mono WAV → analyze
- Global fallbacks:
  - If MP4 conversion fails → direct ffmpeg downmix to WAV
  - If IAB downmix ffmpeg fails → use raw Conversion Tool WAV
